Package com.pb.aquavis.emfac2011

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Emfac2011Data
    The AbstractEmfac2011Data class is used to provide data used to modify the EMFAC2011 SG input file.
    Emfac2011InputFileCreator
    The InputTemplateCreator class is used to build an adjusted input file used for running the EMFAC2011 SG model.
    Emfac2011Properties
    The Emfac2011Properties holds the properties used by the various classes in this package.
    Emfac2011Runner
    The Emfac2011Runner class is used to generate an EMFAC2011 SG input file adjusted for travel demand model results, and then run (via the end user) the EMFAC2011 SG model using those inputs.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Emfac2011SpeedCategory
    The EmfacSpeedClass enum represents the speed categories used in the EMFAC2011 model.
    Emfac2011VehicleType
    The EmfacVehicleType enum represents the EMFAC2011 vehicle types.
